<lb n="1118a06" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>佛說當來變經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="1118a07" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1118a08" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="1118002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（西晉…譯））十一字＝（（竺法護譯））四字【宋】【宮】，（（西晉三藏法師竺法護譯））十字【元】【明】，〔西晉…譯〕－【聖】</note><app n="1118002" word-count="11"><lem wit="【大】">西晉月氏國三藏竺法護譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">竺法護譯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">西晉三藏法師竺法護譯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="1118a09" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT12p1118a0901">聞如是：</p><p id="pT12p1118a0904" place="inline">一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園，與
<lb n="1118a10" ed="T"/>大比丘眾俱，比丘五百及諸菩薩。</p>
<lb n="1118a11" ed="T"/><p id="pT12p1118a1101">爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「將來之世，當有比丘，因
<lb n="1118a12" ed="T"/>有一法不從法化，令法毀滅，不得長益。何謂
<lb n="1118a13" ed="T"/>為一？不護禁戒，不能守心，不修智慧，放逸其
<lb n="1118a14" ed="T"/>意，唯求<note n="1118003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善＝華【宮】</note><app n="1118003"><lem wit="【大】">善</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">華</rdg></app>名不順道教，不肯<note n="1118004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勤＝謹【宋】【元】</note><app n="1118004"><lem wit="【大】">勤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">謹</rdg></app>慕度世之
<lb n="1118a15" ed="T"/>業。是為一事，令法毀滅。」</p>
<lb n="1118a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT12p1118a1601">佛告比丘：「復有二事，令法毀滅。何謂為二？一、
<lb n="1118a17" ed="T"/>不護禁戒，不攝其心，不修智慧，畜妻養子放
<lb n="1118a18" ed="T"/>心恣意，賈作治<note n="1118005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝產【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生＝產【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118005"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">產</rdg></app>以<note n="1118006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">共相＝相供【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">共相＝相供【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118006"><lem wit="【大】">共相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">相供</rdg></app>活。二、伴黨相著
<lb n="1118a19" ed="T"/>憎奉法者，欲令<note n="1118007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陷＝墜【宮】</note><app n="1118007"><lem wit="【大】">陷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">墜</rdg></app>墮故為言<note n="1118008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">義＝儀【三】，議【宮】</note><note n="1118008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">義＝儀【宋】【元】【明】，＝議【宮】</note><app n="1118008"><lem wit="【大】">義</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">儀</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">議</rdg></app>，謂之<note n="1118009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諛＝諭【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1118009"><lem wit="【大】">諛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">諭</rdg></app>諂；
<lb n="1118a20" ed="T"/><note n="1118010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">內＋（私）【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">內＋（私）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118010"><lem wit="【大】">內</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">內私</rdg></app>犯惡<note n="1118011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔行〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔行〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118011"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>外<note n="1118012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佯＝揚【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佯＝揚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118012"><lem wit="【大】">佯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">揚</rdg></app>清白。是為二事，令法毀
<lb n="1118a21" ed="T"/>滅。」</p>
<lb n="1118a22" ed="T"/><p id="pT12p1118a2201">佛告<note n="1118013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="1118013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔諸〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="1118013"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>比丘：「復有三事，令法毀滅。何謂為
<lb n="1118a23" ed="T"/>三？一、既不護<note n="1118014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔禁〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔禁〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118014"><lem wit="【大】">禁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="1118015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">戒＝病【宋】，〔戒〕－【聖】</note><app n="1118015"><lem wit="【大】">戒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">病</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app>，不能攝心，不修<note n="1118016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智慧＝經義【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智慧＝經義【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118016"><lem wit="【大】">智慧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">經義</rdg></app>。二、
<lb n="1118a24" ed="T"/><note n="1118017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝白【聖】</note><app n="1118017"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">白</rdg></app>讀文字不<note n="1118018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">識＝諦【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">識＝諦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118018"><lem wit="【大】">識</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">諦</rdg></app>句<note n="1118019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">逗＝讀【宋】</note><app n="1118019"><lem wit="【大】">逗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">讀</rdg></app>，以上著下、以下著上，
<lb n="1118a25" ed="T"/>頭尾顛倒，不能解了義之所歸，自以為是。三、
<lb n="1118a26" ed="T"/>明者呵之不從其教，反懷瞋恨，謂相嫉&CB00107;。<note n="1118020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">識義＝議識【聖】</note><app n="1118020"><lem wit="【大】">識
<lb n="1118a27" ed="T"/>義</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">議識</rdg></app>者少，多不別理<note n="1118021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">咸＝成【元】</note><app n="1118021"><lem wit="【大】">咸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">成</rdg></app><note n="1118022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">云＝自【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">云＝自【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118022"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">自</rdg></app>為是。是為三事，令
<lb n="1118a28" ed="T"/>法毀滅。」</p>
<lb n="1118a29" ed="T"/><p id="pT12p1118a2901">佛告<app type="＊" source="1118013"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>比丘：「復有四事，令法毀滅。何謂為
<pb n="1118b" id="T12.0395.1118b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1118b01" ed="T"/>四？一、將來比丘，<note n="1118023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（已捨…業））十二字＝（（捨空閑處修道之業））八字【聖】</note><app n="1118023" word-count="12"><lem wit="【大】">已捨家<note n="1118024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔業〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔業〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118024"><lem wit="【大】">業</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>在空閑處，不修
<lb n="1118b02" ed="T"/>道業</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">捨空閑處修道之業</rdg></app>。二、&CB00540;遊人間憒&CB00436;之中，行<note n="1118025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">來＋（比丘）【三】【聖】</note><note n="1118025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來＋（比丘）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="1118025"><lem wit="【大】">來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】">來比丘</rdg></app>談言，求好
<lb n="1118b03" ed="T"/>袈裟五色之服。三、高<note n="1118026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聽＝望【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聽＝望【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118026"><lem wit="【大】">聽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">望</rdg></app>遠視以為綺<note n="1118027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雅＝飾【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">雅＝飾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118027"><lem wit="【大】">雅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">飾</rdg></app>，自
<lb n="1118b04" ed="T"/>以高德無能及者，以雜<note n="1118028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">碎＋（之）【元】【明】</note><app n="1118028"><lem wit="【大】">碎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">碎之</rdg></app>智<note n="1118029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔比〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1118029"><lem wit="【大】">比</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>日月<note n="1118030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之明＝比丘【宋】，之比丘【元】，〔之明〕－【宮】</note><note n="1118030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之明＝比丘【宋】，＝之比丘【元】，〔之明〕－【宮】</note><app n="1118030"><lem wit="【大】">之明</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">比丘</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">之比丘</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>——
<lb n="1118b05" ed="T"/>畜已！四、不攝三事，不護根門，行婦女間，宣文
<lb n="1118b06" ed="T"/>飾辭多言合<note n="1118031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">偶＝禍【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1118031"><lem wit="【大】">偶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">禍</rdg></app>，以動人心，使清變濁；身行
<lb n="1118b07" ed="T"/>荒亂，正法廢遲。是為四事，令法毀滅。」</p>
<lb n="1118b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT12p1118b0801">佛告比丘：「復有五事，令法毀滅。何謂為五？
<lb n="1118b09" ed="T"/><note n="1118032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118032"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>、或有比丘，本以法故出家修道，廢深經教
<lb n="1118b10" ed="T"/>十二因緣、三十七品，方等深妙玄虛之慧、智
<lb n="1118b11" ed="T"/>度無極、善權方便、空無相願至化之<note n="1118033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">節＝第【聖】</note><app n="1118033"><lem wit="【大】">節</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">第</rdg></app>。二、
<lb n="1118b12" ed="T"/>反習雜句淺<note n="1118034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔末〕－【宮】</note><app n="1118034"><lem wit="【大】">末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>小<note n="1118035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（輩）【宮】</note><app n="1118035"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">經輩</rdg></app>，世俗行故。<note n="1118036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝三【三】</note><note n="1118036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王＝三【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="1118036"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">三</rdg></app>者經典，
<lb n="1118b13" ed="T"/>亂道之原，好講此業，易解世事，趣得人心令
<lb n="1118b14" ed="T"/>其歡<note n="1118037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喜＝悅【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喜＝悅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118037"><lem wit="【大】">喜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">悅</rdg></app>，因致名聞。<note n="1118038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三〕－【宋】【宮】，三＝四【元】【明】</note><app n="1118038"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">&lac;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">四</rdg></app>、新聞法人、淺解之士，
<lb n="1118b15" ed="T"/>意用妙快；深達之<note n="1118039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">士＝人【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">士＝人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118039"><lem wit="【大】">士</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">人</rdg></app>，不用為<note n="1118040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佳＝法【聖】</note><app n="1118040"><lem wit="【大】">佳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">法</rdg></app>。<note n="1118041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔四〕－【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔四〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118041"><lem wit="【大】">四</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app>、天龍鬼
<lb n="1118b16" ed="T"/>神不以為喜，心懷悒慼口<note n="1118042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">發斯＝能發【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">發斯＝能發【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118042"><lem wit="【大】">發斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">能發</rdg></app>言：『大法欲滅，
<lb n="1118b17" ed="T"/>故使其然。』捨妙<note n="1118043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法化＝化法【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法化＝化法【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118043"><lem wit="【大】">法化</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">化法</rdg></app>，反宣雜句。諸天流淚，速
<lb n="1118b18" ed="T"/>逝而去。五、<note n="1118044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">由＋（說）【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">由＋（說）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118044"><lem wit="【大】">由</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">由說</rdg></app>是正法稍稍見捨，無精修者。是
<lb n="1118b19" ed="T"/>為五事，令法毀滅。」</p>
<lb n="1118b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT12p1118b2001">佛告比丘：「吾滅度後，有此邪事十<note n="1118045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">五＝四【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">五＝四【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118045"><lem wit="【大】">五</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">四</rdg></app>之亂，令
<lb n="1118b21" ed="T"/>法毀滅，一何痛哉！若有比丘欲諦學道，棄捐
<lb n="1118b22" ed="T"/>綺飾、不求名聞、質<note n="1118046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">朴＝科【三】</note><note n="1118046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">朴＝科【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="1118046"><lem wit="【大】">朴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">科</rdg></app>守真、宣傳正經。佛之雅
<lb n="1118b23" ed="T"/>典深法之<note n="1118047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">化＝辭【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">化＝辭【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118047"><lem wit="【大】">化</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">辭</rdg></app>不用多言，案<note n="1118048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">本說＝其本【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">本說＝其本【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118048"><lem wit="【大】">本說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">其本</rdg></app>經不捨正
<lb n="1118b24" ed="T"/>句，希言屢中不失佛意。&CB00308;衣趣食，得美不甘；
<lb n="1118b25" ed="T"/>得&CB00308;不<note n="1118049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惡＝&CB01158;【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1118049"><lem wit="【大】">惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">&CB01158;</rdg></app>。衣食好醜，隨施者意，不以瞋喜。
<lb n="1118b26" ed="T"/><note n="1118050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">攝＝護【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">攝＝護【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118050"><lem wit="【大】">攝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">護</rdg></app>身、口、意守諸根門，不違佛教。<note n="1118051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">念＝壽【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念＝壽【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118051"><lem wit="【大】">念</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">壽</rdg></app>命甚<note n="1118052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">矩＝短【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">矩＝短【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】【CB】</note><app n="1118052"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">短</lem><rdg wit="【大】">矩</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">短</rdg></app>，
<lb n="1118b27" ed="T"/>恍<note n="1118053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惚＝忽【聖】</note><app n="1118053"><lem wit="【大】">惚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">忽</rdg></app><note n="1118054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118054"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">已</rdg></app>過，如夢所見，覺不知<note n="1118055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">處＝虛【宋】</note><app n="1118055"><lem wit="【大】">處</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">虛</rdg></app>。三塗之難，
<lb n="1118b28" ed="T"/>不可稱計，勤修佛法猶救頭然。五戒、十善、六
<lb n="1118b29" ed="T"/>度無極，四等、四恩、智慧、善權咸可<note n="1118056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">精＝修【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">精＝修【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118056"><lem wit="【大】">精</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">修</rdg></app>行。<note n="1118057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雖＋（復後生）【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">雖＋（復後生）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118057"><lem wit="【大】">雖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雖復後生</rdg></app>
<pb n="1118c" id="T12.0395.1118c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1118c01" ed="T"/>不值佛世，出家為道，學不唐捐，<note n="1118058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">平＝卒【宮】</note><app n="1118058"><lem wit="【大】">平</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">卒</rdg></app>其本心，愍
<lb n="1118c02" ed="T"/><note n="1118059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">念＝哀【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念＝哀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118059"><lem wit="【大】">念</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">哀</rdg></app>一切，十方蒙恩。」</p><p id="pT12p1118c0208" place="inline">佛說如是，諸比丘悲喜前
<lb n="1118c03" ed="T"/>自歸佛，作禮而去。</p></div1>
<lb n="1118c04" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><title>佛說當來變經</title></jhead></juan>
